              "fill": "#A1A1AAFF",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 720,
              "content": "Deep dive into the Flutter rendering pipeline and how to build performant custom widgets using RenderObject. We'll cover the full lifecycle — from constraints to painting — with a real-world example.",
